---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Alex Wilson" description="Alex Wilson writes about the things he's trying to understand.">
  <section class="intro">
    <h1>About</h1>

    <p class="intro__text">
      This is the website of Alex Wilson. Here you will find my musings about the world, mostly intended for myself, but some of which others may find interesting.
    </p>
    <p>
    I'm on twitter @awlego; my dms are open. You can also reach me at @awlego many places around the internet. Say hi! I respond to almost all good faith correspondance.
    </p>
  </section>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <div class="post__content">
    <h2>Beliefs</h2>
    <p>
    I believe in play.
    </p>
    <p>
    I believe in seeking slack.
    </p>
    <p>
    I believe in looking at things with enchanted eyes — choosing to see wonder, choosing to be delighted.
    </p>
    <p>
    I believe in the seasons. There are seasons of growth, seasons of sadness, seasons of quiet, seasons of bountiful joy and harvest. Friendships have seasons. Careers have seasons. Selves have seasons.
    </p>
    <p>
    I believe in sleeping in.
    </p>
    <p>
    I believe in food that makes "mmmmmmmm" escape my lips.
    </p>
    <p>
    I believe in the importance of friendship.
    </p>
    <p>
    I believe in laughter and in serious thought.
    </p>
    <p>
    I believe in interpretting words and actions charitably.
    </p>
    <p>
    I believe there are many lives worth living.
    </p>
    <p>
    I believe in focusing on what you want to see more of in the world. Joke about the outcomes you want to see in the world. 
    </p>
    <p>
    I believe the meaning of life is to love and to be loved.
    </p>
    </ul>

    <h2>Elsewhere</h2>

    <ul>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/awlego" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://twitter.com/awlego" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Twitter</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <footer class="about-footer">
    <p>I am not under any NDA or other agreement that would preclude me from revealing that such an agreement exists.</p>
  </footer>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  h2 + .section-subtitle {
    display: block;
    margin-top: -0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .about-footer {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border, #e0e0e0);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted, #666);
  }

  .about-footer p {
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
